\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>American Standard Shop is a Southern California\u2013based apparel company dedicated to strengthening the U.S. textile industry through modern manufacturing, responsible sourcing, and fast, reliable production.<\/p><p>As a certified small business listed on SAM.gov and Cal eProcure, we proudly support federal, state, and local procurement programs. Our products are trusted by government agencies, contractors, corporations, and organizations that value compliance, durability, and American-made craftsmanship.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-85de1ad e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"85de1ad\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1fdcbab e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1fdcbab\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6045f05 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6045f05\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Our Mission<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d0ceb4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3d0ceb4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>To deliver high-quality U.S.-made uniforms, polos, workwear, and blanks with unmatched turnaround time \u2014 while helping rebuild and protect America\u2019s textile supply chain.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class